[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

You open with a Weak 2-Bid, 2\D. Partner responds 2NT. What do you say next? 

The 2NT bid is forcing and you have better than a minimum. You show your "feature" by bidding 3\H. Partner now bids 3NT which you naturally pass.}

